    </ul>
  </nav>

  <div class="navbar">
    <a href="/emotion.html" class="logo">
      <img src="/assets/emotion-centre-logo-horizontal.png" alt="" class="mobile-logo-img" />
    </a>
    <ul>
      <!-- <li>
                        <a href="#contact">
                            <button class="btn-outline">Contact</button>
                        </a>
                    </li> -->
      <li><a href="/index.html">{'< Family Tree'}</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <header id="emotion-home">
    <div class="overlay"></div>
    <div class="header-content">
      <h1>Emotion Centre</h1>
      <p>Emotion Centre is a welcoming, quiet, screen-free nook for book lovers of all ages.</p>
      <a href="#contact">
        <button class="btn-outline">Contact</button>
      </a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="about container">
    <img src="/assets/emotion-centre-logo.png" alt="" />
    <p>
      Emotion Centre is a welcoming, quiet, screen-free nook for book lovers of all ages. Emerging
      out of the yearsof experience that the psychotherapists at Family Tree have in working with
      children and their parents, we invite you to attend to your emotional internal world through
      stories and pictures. <br />
      Often, this process of focusing and a slower pace is calming and enlivening, especially in today’s
      digital world where our attention span is drastically shrinking. If you are a parent and would
      like to help your child develop a reading habit, or you would like to have time with your child
      away from digital devices (including your own), this is the place to be.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="reasons">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="heading">We reach out to books for many reasons:</p>
      <div class="cards">
        <div class="card">
          <img src="/assets/pin.png" alt="Emotion Centre Icon" />
          <p>To learn something</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="/assets/pin.png" alt="Emotion Centre Icon" />
          <p>To feel something</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="/assets/pin.png" alt="Emotion Centre Icon" />
          <p>To avoid feeling something</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="/assets/pin.png" alt="Emotion Centre Icon" />
          <p>To fill up time</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="/assets/pin.png" alt="Emotion Centre Icon" />
          <p>To laugh</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="emotion-info container">
    <img src="/assets/no-phone.png" alt="" />
    <p class="heading">
      Want to raise HAPPY, SUCCESSFUL kids? <br />
      ‘WAIT AS LONG AS POSSIBLE TO GIVE THEM A PHONE', says a Yale expert Laurie Santos.
    </p>
    <div class="row">
      <p>
        At Emotion Centre, the booksare curated and catalogued by emotional themes, not by author
        reading age ortitle.
      </p>
      <img src="/assets/book-tent.png" alt="" />
      <p>
        Emotion Centre also offers brief therapeutic work through the use of stories with children
        under 11 years of age. We work with a lowsliding fee scale and offer individual
        psychotherapy for children.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer id="contact">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="left">
        <p>Have a Query?</p>
        <p>
          Contact us at - <a href="tel:9873333542">9873333542</a> / <a href="tel:9013962794"
            >9013962794</a
          > / <a href="tel:+91-11-26107477">+91-11-26107477</a>
        </p>
        <p>
          For more details, contact Shweta Dharamdasani at <a
            href="mailto:emotioncentredelhi@gmail.com">emotioncentredelhi@gmail.com</a
          >
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="right">
        <a href="/emotion.html">
          <img src="/assets/emotion-centre-logo.png" alt="" />
        </a>
        <p>
          Follow us on: <a
            href="https://www.instagram.com/emotioncentre/"
            target="_blank"
            class="insta">Instagram</a
          >
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script src="emotion-script.js" defer async></script>
</Layout>
